---
title: Classic Shortbread perfect for sharing
description: A classic dessert of Scottish origin baked to perfection made with plenty of butter.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_RA_R2501_W35_IE_IEA28739-3_Main__4high-f56de2d9.jpg
